Clifford Mollison https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clifford_Mollison 0 Clifford Lely Mollison (30 March 1897 – 4 June 1986) was a British film and television actor. He was married to the actress Avril Wheatley. His younger brother was the actor Henry Mollison. Clifford_Lely_Mollison ( 30_March_1897 – 4_June_1986 ) was a_British_film_and_television_actor .
